    <abstract>
      <t>The Real Time Streaming Protocol, or RTSP, is an application-level protocol for control over the delivery of data with real-time properties.  RTSP provides an extensible framework to enable controlled, on-demand delivery of real-time data, such as audio and video. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
	 </t>
